headline: Is Kellanova Still Attractive After Its Transformation Into a Global Snacking Powerhouse?
summary: Wondering if Kellanova at around $83 a share is still a tasty buy or if most of the upside has already been served up? Let us unpack what the current price is really baking in. The stock has slipped slightly in the very short term, down 0.6% over the last week and 0.1% over the last month, but it is still up 2.6% year to date and has delivered 69.2% over five years. Recently, investors have been reacting to Kellanova's ongoing transformation into a more focused global snacking business,...
